dc_description_s: Relief shown by 5 feet contour interval, and spot heights. Map shows district, municipal or township, and property boundaries. "Cadastral boundaries as shown on this map do not in any way affect the boundaries shown in Registered Titles." Includes ancillary sheet index. "Heights in feet." "Surveyed (March 1964) and drawn (July 1965) by the Department of Lands and Surveys, Uganda." "The representation on this map of a road, track or footpath is no evidence of the existence of a right of way." "200-8-65." ©Copyright Uganda Government 1965.
dc_creator_sm: Uganda. Department of Lands and Surveys
